    "details": {
      "biography": "<p>1&rsquo; tall, winged humanoids, related to pixies and elves. They are shy, but driven by curiosity and their odd sense of humour.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Curse: </strong>Five sprites can collectively curse a target (no attack roll; Mental save). The effect is determined by the referee, but will always be used to comical effect (e.g. target trips, target&rsquo;s nose grows).</li>\n<li><strong>Pranksters:</strong> Even if attacked, sprites have no interest in killing, merely in making practical jokes.</li>\n</ul>",
